data.description: Captivating views of Lake Pend Oreille and surrounding Selkirk mountains greet you from every window in this custom log home Featuring grand logs, a custom river rock fireplace, a main level master suite & a basement master suite with 2 additional rooms on 8+ acres This exquisitely updated home, encompasses a chefs kitchen with quartzite countertops & JENNAIR appliance suite Enjoy the sunsets on the wrap around deck while entertaining or from your walkout finished basement With nearby Hawkins public boat launch, two hidden beaches they allow you to set off into the water on your boat or paddle board, and enjoy Lake Pend Oreille.
